{"tid":1190914,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你6月9日出遊行，係基於對件事點理解？係有咩目的想達到？","createTime":"2019-06-07T15:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T03:25:51.000Z","uid":76885,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9c0a733842813aa08342f68364ca098a31a15a","tid":1190914,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n之前我自己一直唔知啲細節。<br />\n一直想，如果6月9日出，係明清楚成件事既邏輯，知自己反啲咩、為咩目的先出。<br />\n<br />\n今朝見到律師公會懶人包：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85-%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88-%E7%B0%A1%E6%98%93%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97-%E8%A7%A3%E7%AD%94%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-24-%E5%80%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C/?fbclid=IwAR3Sl-VNa3K-y46n-rgD6vle7d0H4sIXsNhNg-VFzkiq9jCiZ3-v3fxY5R8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%2587%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BD%2588-%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258D%2597-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%25AD%2594%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-24-%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Sl-VNa3K-y46n-rgD6vle7d0H4sIXsNhNg-VFzkiq9jCiZ3-v3fxY5R8&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8umHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=c82a7cfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%2587%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BD%2588-%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258D%2597-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%25AD%2594%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-24-%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Sl-VNa3K-y46n-rgD6vle7d0H4sIXsNhNg-VFzkiq9jCiZ3-v3fxY5R8&h=e2b2b3c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85-%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88-%E7%B0%A1%E6%98%93%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97-%E8%A7%A3%E7%AD%94%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-24-%E5%80%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C/?fbclid=IwAR3Sl-VNa3K-y46n-rgD6vle7d0H4sIXsNhNg-VFzkiq9jCiZ3-v3fxY5R8</a><br />\n<br />\n特別留意到第五項。<br />\n然後聽人講，而而家大概理解係：<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例唔係一種先前立基本法時既漏洞。<br />\n而係草基本法既人，為落實一國兩制；衡量利害後，決定唔納中國地區入逃犯條例。<br />\n有其他國家有納，而佢地都有合理原因。<br />\n<br />\n而當時中國無納，可能因為兩地權力失衡問題？<br />\n其次係中國既法治未完善、不可信。<br />\n<br />\n而由當時到而家，情況無變，甚至有變壞？<br />\n所以更加唔應該喺而家呢個時期立。<br />\n<br />\n唔係永遠唔納。<br />\n而係中共有日唔再破壞一國兩制，而且佢有真正法治時，就可以納。<br />\n<br />\n唔係香港人要反共，而係中共自己未合格、未夠條件去被納入。<br />\n<br />\n而6月9日，遊行，最低限度，就係為反映自己作為香港一分子既民意？<br />\n<br />\n其他升級行動，假如有，就係一啲，為反映民意之上既其他目的。就會要其他justification。<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n暫時我自己會咁諗。<br />\n有無咩地方修正或補充？<br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n你呢？<br />\n你對件事既理解係點？<br />\n有咩目的想達到？"},{"pid":"f67f582cf24b4d09ba24eab68f71bde47b288704","tid":1190914,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5906d5bbcb440cc76a0733f48d790403579537","tid":1190914,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"<em>林鄭集團為推《逃犯條例》攻擊中國司法體制！習新時代中國特色法治要堅決抵制司法獨立，由rule of law, rule by law 說起</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BGGUp87epsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBGGUp87epsA&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8umHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=5af71f16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BGGUp87epsA</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左呢段。<br />\n感覺係，如果中共領導人繼續用具中國特式既方針。<br />\n中共同香港永遠唔可以喺法律上行太埋。<br />\n否則香港就必然由Rule of law變成Rule by law。<br />\n<br />\n法治（英語：rule of law），是與人治相反之概念。與法制不同，法治指以民意授權為前提和基礎立法，以嚴格依法管治國家為核心，以制約權力為關鍵的社會管理機制、社會活動方式和社會秩序狀態。法治的內涵，不單是要求所有人民守法，更側重於法律對政府權力的控制和拘束。<br />\n<br />\n以法而治（英語：rule by law），又稱為以法管治、以法制民，為區別與法治，而簡稱法制。是一種對法律存在目的的認識和信念，即法律是政府管理國家、管理社會的工具，制定法律以管束人民。把法律當做統治工具的政府會侵犯公民權利，而對應的法律應被廢除並停止執行。以法統治與保護民主自由的法治也是有區別的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/法治\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8umHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=bf03c826\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/法治</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/以法而治\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%BB%A5%E6%B3%95%E8%80%8C%E6%B2%BB&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8umHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=fe11b079\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/以法而治</a>"}]}